metadata.name: The Truth #1
metadata.description: Number Is You is an NFT collection created by 16 y.o and 18 y.o artists of Z'SH production, who began making creative works with their eldest sister in 2016. The collection consists of 10 unique NFTs. 10 NFTs is based on a quote about the number from philosopher Pythagoras, which is 'Number rules the universe' The number is the soul of time and space in the universe. So who is going to be the number?
